snippet.title: Barbie In The Twelve Dancing Princesses [27] PS2 Longplay
snippet.description:
Barbie in the 12 Dancing Princesses is a 2006 action game based on the movie of the same name. In this game, Barbie portrays Genevieve, 1 of 12 sisters who live happily with their father the king. After a run-in with the king's cousin, the girls lost the ability to dance and must get it back to save their father's life.

For more Barbie games: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBA7nqyBa-vycNP973v38ljYWVysqjz3u
For more PS2 Longplays: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FRaGChDC00E&list=PLBA7nqyBa-vw7XiVAYPQgYzlKizalWP3n
